<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    
    <title>{{ title or site.name }}</title>
    <meta name="description" content="{{ description or site.description }}">
    <link rel="canonical" href="{{ site.url }}{{ page.url }}">

    <meta property="og:type" content="website">
    <meta property="og:title" content="{{ title or site.name }}">
    <meta property="og:description" content="daily mandated celestial directives. zero-latency inevitable truths.">
    <meta property="og:image" content="{{ site.url }}{{ site.og_image }}">

    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
    <meta name="twitter:title" content="{{ title }}">
    
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1 style="text-align: center; text-transform: lowercase;">{{ site.name }}</h1>
    </header>
    
    <main>
        {{ content | safe }}
    </main>

    <footer class="site-footer">
        <hr class="divider">
        <p>this report is generated automatically by the <strong>central inevitability engine</strong>.</p>
        <p>all predictions are deterministic and legally binding in at least three dimensions. failure to comply with celestial directives may result in unexpected existential drift.</p>
        <p>
            <a href="{{ site.repo }}">source protocol</a> | 
            authorized by <span class="author">{{ site.author }}</span> | 
            © {{ "now" | date("YYYY") }} universal archive
        </p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>